<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[ في الفرنسية]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>Le Kalam( theologie dogmatique ou rationnelle musulmane )<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
